                  </hi>. I am a pawnbroker, at Hounslow. The pillow-case was pawned with me, on the 29th of April, and the handker<lb></lb>chief on the 9th of May, both by the prisoner, in her own name.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was very short of money, and took the handker<lb></lb>chief, not intending to keep it, but to replace it.</p>
